== Lineage == Mikashikiyahime was the sister of {{ill|Nagasunehiko|ja|長髄彦}} and the wife of {{ill|Nigihayahi|ja|饒速日命|lt=Nigihayahi no Mikoto}}. Together, they had a son, {{ill|Umashimaji no Mikoto|ja|宇摩志麻遅命}}, who became the ancestral deity of the {{ill|Mononobe clan|ja|物部氏}} and {{ill|Hozumi clan|ja|穂積氏}}.<ref name="#3"/>
== Shrines == Mikashikiyahime is enshrined at several locations: * {{ill|Ishikiri Tsurugiya Shrine|ja|石切剣箭神社}}: Within the {{ill|Upper Shrine (Ishikiri Tsurugiya Shrine)|ja|石切剣箭神社#上之社}}, specifically at the Tomireisha and {{ill|Fudō Shrine|ja|婦道神社}} (Higashi-Osaka City, Osaka Prefecture). * {{ill|Yataza Kushitama Hikojinja|ja|矢田坐久志玉比古神社}} * {{ill|Kushitama Hime-no-Mikoto Shrine|ja|櫛玉比女命神社}}
