== Lineage == Mikashikiyahime was the sister of {{ill|Nagasunehiko|ja|長髄彦|12=draft}} and the wife of {{ill|Nigihayahi|ja|饒速日命|lt=Nigihayahi no Mikoto|12=draft}}. Together, they had a son, {{ill|Umashimaji no Mikoto|ja|宇摩志麻遅命|12=draft}}, who became the ancestral deity of the {{ill|Mononobe clan|ja|物部氏|12=draft}} and {{ill|Hozumi clan|ja|穂積氏|12=draft}}.<ref name="#3"/>
